{
  "texts": [
    "Publications that were unsuitable, such as those lacking thematic relevance or with a different focus, were excluded from further evaluation.",
    "To supplement the literature search, reference mining was used to identify additional publications.",
    "This involved analyzing the reference lists of the selected articles to identify related sources.",
    "A detailed overview of the search strategy, including the inclusion and exclusion criteria, can be found in the Supplementary Material.",
    "Given the emergent nature of DeSci, preprint publications were also included in the search strategy to enable a representation of the most current research findings."
  ]
}